{"tid":667990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仆街又阻人放工】屯門公路多車相撞15人傷 入屯門車龍4公里","createTime":"2018-05-17T08:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T09:52:20.000Z","uid":60281,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a74ea8e26d1c66f1be1135dd63ca26ae5bd233aa","tid":667990,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n深井屯門公路向屯門方向近浪翠園，下午3時20分發生交通意外。據報現場多部車輛相撞，當中涉及一部旅遊巴與一輛貨車，初步最少15人受傷。大批救援人員正在現場拯救。<br />\n<br />\n受交通意外影響，屯門公路往屯門方向近浪翠園的部份行車線仍然封閉，駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。現時在屯門公路往屯門方向的車龍龍尾至4公里外的汀九橋。"},{"pid":"1aadda4ed3e347aa82a828543fda3247ca49a86a","tid":667990,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c23b3501a3288145ea1e8c6d7942c4614c5e8d","tid":667990,"uid":42182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a74ea8e26d1c66f1be1135dd63ca26ae5bd233aa","tid":667990,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n深井屯門公路向屯門方向近浪翠園，下午3時20分發生交通意外。據報現場多部車輛相撞，當中涉及一部旅遊巴與一輛貨車，初步最少15人受傷。大批救援人員正在現場拯救。<br />\n<br />\n受交通意外影響，屯門公路往屯門方向近浪翠園的部份行車線仍然封閉，駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。現時在屯門公路往屯門方向的車龍龍尾至4公里外的汀九橋。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"日夜都塞"},{"pid":"baa39f14651e830565f9c11b660429a10185229b","tid":667990,"uid":45772,"lik